@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Move Bullet Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant MoveBulletCommand
participant RecordList
participant Record
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: movebullet RECORD_INDEX FROM TO
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: MoveBulletCommand
Resumake -> MoveBulletCommand: execute(list)
MoveBulletCommand -> RecordList: getRecord(recordIndex)
MoveBulletCommand -> Record: moveBullet(fromIndex, toIndex)
MoveBulletCommand -> Ui: show move status
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
